data.description: This beautifully kept home resides in the desirable 55+ community of Rainbow Ridge!  Inside this loveable 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom manufactured home you will find an open layout where the living area flows nicely into the spacious kitchen.  Outside is a large covered patio for relaxing and there is also a 80sft shed with power for additional storage or a room to enjoy your hobbies. Amenities included are a community pool, hot tub and events center. (NO RENTALS ALLOWED, All offers contingent upon the required HOA age verification and application.)
